                    .format("csv")
                    .option("inferSchema", "true")
                    .option("header", "true")
                    .load("/data/Raw/NetworkInformations/all_chain_network_info.csv")

                    , avg($"sigma").alias("sigma"), avg($"density").alias("density"))

def histDfCreator(resDf :org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame , bucket :Int, method :String, epoch :String, io :String) :org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = {
    
    val (startValues,degree) = rawResDf.filter($"method" === method && $"epoch" === epoch && $"in/out" === io).select($"degrees").map(v => v.getDouble(0)).rdd.histogram(bucket)
    val zippedValues = startValues.map(_.toInt).zip(degree)
    val rowRDD = zippedValues.map( value => HistRow(value._1,value._2))
    val histDf = spark.createDataFrame(rowRDD)
    return histDf
}
